.DT
set_vote_duration
Disk World creator help
set_vote_duration

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_vote_duration -  This function is used to set the normal vote and election duration.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_vote_duration(int duration)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^duraction%^RESET%^ - The number of seconds the vote should be open.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/voting_room.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is used to set the normal vote and election duration. It can
be overridden when calling add_vote. If it is not set and no duration is
given in add_vote then the default value of DEFAULT_VOTE_DURATION is used.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_vote()

.EP

